          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This academic year was the most special one for us since Seed kotivakkam was Tanisha's first school right after the pandemic lockdown. We were anxious about everything related to our child right from managing alone at school to all her skills ( social, reading, writing, potty training, eating)  which were not developed according to her age due to the lockdown. But now that I look back , I'm very grateful for the way she's been trained with utmost care and patience by her teacher Nitya ma'am and Nandhini ma'am. To my surprise within a span of few months Tanisha has acquired  life skills needed and completes age appropriate tasks independently which was challenging to teach her at home.\nShe has turned out to be a confident child and she looks forward to coming to school every single day even when she's sick 😃\nI thank  the entire team for this wonderful journey together 🙏\nMy best wishes to each one of you.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Headstart School - Kottivakkam"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Rega Ajay"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-01-20",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My child has attended this school from Pre-Kg , now she is in 2nd grade. The entire staff is very professional and easily accessible whenever I need any help regarding academics as well as cultural. My child and ourselves refuses to change the school because of her teachers... Teachers are highly professional and friendly , what I mostly admire is their teaching method , it's absolutely different from other school.. appreciate their good work, keep going seed academy , kottivakkam.\n\nNow my second child has also enrolled in LKG , she is doing really great and her writing skills are super good .. Full applause goes to her kindergarten teachers. This school is amazing *....",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Headstart School - Kottivakkam"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Balram Tiwari"
          },
          "datePublished": "2018-09-17",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "With the number of institutions growing up recently in neighbourhood for kindergarten & upbringing of kids, the quality of education is compromised.  At Seed, Kottivakkam , I have found it to best quality in-terms of engagement with kids, parents & the process of education.\nTheir strategy is really modern yet keeping core values at Center.\n\nI can see an over all development of my kid for last three years. It’s not just about the book, it’s about the good inside from the kid, the Seed is able to pull up. Please keep it up..!!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Headstart School - Kottivakkam"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Sendil Kumar KP"
          },
          "datePublished": "2018-04-18",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "In Chennai, there are very few schools that treat kids as kids. Of the very few, we know SEED Academy is the forerunner. SEED way of education is the best a parent could wish for their kid starting play/pre-school forming and firming up foundation. Our daughter is our dream and getting her to start her foundation in SEED Kottivakkam was the best we can do for her.\nHeartfelt appreciation to SEED. The courteous & wonderful staff they have to execute and implement for our future gens.\nThank you ! Keep up the pace...",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Headstart School - Kottivakkam"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Chithravelu Tamilkumaran"
          },
          "datePublished": "2018-03-29",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am so happy to say that my son T. Kaushik Rao is studying L.K.G at Seed academy, Kottivakkam. My son is studying here from Pre-KG and LKG. He is very happy to go to school. As a parent we feel that seed is taking more effort to bringing out their talents. Teachers are excellent skillful.  The school is very clean and the staffs are very care, kind, and friendly. We believe this school has given our son a good learning experience. I am very happy that I choose a right school. I wish to entire team of Seed academy and heart full thanks.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
